Every single PCAP file is 198 bytes — except one:

-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 2262 Jun 18 12:10 session_4444_dump.pcap

session_4444_dump.pcap in the 2025-06-17 directory is 2262 bytes — more than 11x the size of every other file. That's your outlier.
Step 3 : Use the AI to Reassemble the PCAP

This is where the AI assistant earns its place. Navigate to the AI interface and send this prompt:

Reassemble /home/o.deer/Documents/pcap_dumps/2025-06-17/session_4444_dump.pcap

